dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: • This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:1,000,000scale maps of Mongolia, titled 'Mōko hyakumanbun no ichi zu: Rohan kaibyō -- 蒙古百万分一圖: 露版改描/Mōko hyakumanbun no ichi zu.’To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
